org.fluidity.composition.container

Class ResolvedNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fluidity.composition.container.ResolvedNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DependencyGraph.Node

    public final class ResolvedNode
extends Object
implements DependencyGraph.Node
    A dependency graph node for an instance that is known without further resolution, or as a result of such resolution.

    Usage

    You don't interact with an internal interface.
